1
00:00:09,114 --> 00:00:13,160
♪I defy heaven, fate,
and so-called immortality♪

2
00:00:13,160 --> 00:00:17,800
♪At last you say
we've been apart too long♪

3
00:00:17,800 --> 00:00:22,840
♪Unwilling, unyielding, I won't let go♪

4
00:00:22,840 --> 00:00:28,000
♪With you, even a dried sea
learns to embrace a stream♪

5
00:00:28,000 --> 00:00:32,415
♪If heaven divides us, I'll reunite us,
with love as our vessel♪

6
00:00:32,415 --> 00:00:37,167
♪If it forbids it, I'll shatter
the absurd Heavenly Dao♪

7
00:00:37,167 --> 00:00:42,400
♪Even if countless stars
turn into my foes♪

8
00:00:42,400 --> 00:00:47,340
♪To grow old with you, we burn
through the end of the long night♪

9
00:00:50,820 --> 00:00:55,760
=Rise Again=

10
00:00:56,144 --> 00:00:58,878
=Episode 5=

11
00:01:10,359 --> 00:01:11,200
A barrier?

12
00:01:28,400 --> 00:01:30,760
Mr. Gu, you've got to help me.

13
00:01:31,200 --> 00:01:32,120
Su Wubing must have

14
00:01:32,120 --> 00:01:33,519
set up a barrier outside the study.

15
00:01:33,519 --> 00:01:34,640
I can't get in at all.

16
00:01:37,200 --> 00:01:37,959
Lin Hai.

17
00:01:38,519 --> 00:01:40,920
I thought you were bringing good news.

18
00:01:43,359 --> 00:01:44,200
Mr. Gu.

19
00:01:44,519 --> 00:01:46,040
He is unbearable.

20
00:01:46,519 --> 00:01:47,799
You've got to take him out for me.

21
00:01:48,200 --> 00:01:48,799
Otherwise,

22
00:01:48,799 --> 00:01:51,079
we'll never get the secret formula
of the Longevity Pill.

23
00:02:00,640 --> 00:02:01,400
Speak.

24
00:02:04,640 --> 00:02:05,640
Get lost first.

25
00:02:06,359 --> 00:02:06,840
Mr. Gu.

26
00:02:08,919 --> 00:02:10,000
I told you to get lost.

27
00:02:29,313 --> 00:02:31,840
(Xue Wuhen, Ancient God Sect)

28
00:02:32,360 --> 00:02:34,240
Show what you've got.

29
00:02:34,439 --> 00:02:36,000
Mr. Gu's a busy man.

30
00:02:36,360 --> 00:02:38,159
No time to chit-chat with you.

31
00:02:43,840 --> 00:02:47,000
Mr. Gu, got a moment now?

32
00:02:48,439 --> 00:02:50,000
Master, please sit.

33
00:03:00,560 --> 00:03:01,400
Please.

34
00:03:06,199 --> 00:03:08,840
I wonder about your cultivation level.

35
00:03:12,080 --> 00:03:15,120
Cultivation has four ranks:
Heaven, Earth, Mystic, and Yellow.

36
00:03:15,199 --> 00:03:17,919
Heaven is the highest,
Yellow the lowest.

37
00:03:18,240 --> 00:03:20,479
Heaven-level masters are
one in a hundred years.

38
00:03:20,520 --> 00:03:22,240
Earth-level, barely a few.

39
00:03:22,520 --> 00:03:23,719
As for Mystic-level,

40
00:03:23,919 --> 00:03:27,319
they're already the best of the best.

41
00:03:27,560 --> 00:03:28,919
Master, and you...?

42
00:03:30,800 --> 00:03:35,080
I've reached early Mystic-level.

43
00:03:36,240 --> 00:03:36,719
Good.

44
00:03:38,080 --> 00:03:38,840
Are you dead yet?

45
00:03:39,919 --> 00:03:40,800
Pay up.

46
00:03:46,800 --> 00:03:49,039
With your cultivation, Master,

47
00:03:49,759 --> 00:03:50,479
I'm impressed.

48
00:03:54,120 --> 00:03:55,159
Hurry up.

49
00:04:00,319 --> 00:04:01,520
Here's 500,000 dollars.

50
00:04:02,039 --> 00:04:03,479
I want someone dead.

51
00:04:05,000 --> 00:04:06,560
(Since ancient times,)

52
00:04:06,759 --> 00:04:09,639
(my ancestors have traveled
through time into this world,)

53
00:04:09,639 --> 00:04:11,479
(founding the Ancient God Sect,)

54
00:04:11,800 --> 00:04:14,800
(just to seize the souls of
the Immortal King and Holy Maiden.)

55
00:04:15,240 --> 00:04:18,160
(Never thought I'd actually
run into them.)

56
00:04:33,759 --> 00:04:35,560
- Pleasure doing business.
- Pleasure doing business.

57
00:04:48,199 --> 00:04:49,120
Master, wait!

58
00:04:50,399 --> 00:04:51,680
Besides having

59
00:04:51,680 --> 00:04:53,680
a sickly old mother,

60
00:04:54,319 --> 00:04:56,399
Su Wubing also has a childhood friend.

61
00:04:58,199 --> 00:05:00,040
Got it.

62
00:05:09,720 --> 00:05:11,040
Dad's illness is cured,

63
00:05:11,800 --> 00:05:14,480
but Gu Yuanbing won't
let it go so easily.

64
00:05:24,759 --> 00:05:26,560
What did my dad say to you yesterday?

65
00:05:28,920 --> 00:05:29,839
Uncle Lin said

66
00:05:32,560 --> 00:05:33,639
you should marry me.

67
00:05:34,759 --> 00:05:35,680
Marry you?

68
00:05:37,199 --> 00:05:38,040
Or rather,

69
00:05:39,560 --> 00:05:40,839
I'm marrying into the Lin family.

70
00:05:43,040 --> 00:05:44,639
Dad wants you to protect me?

71
00:05:50,279 --> 00:05:51,480
I used to think,

72
00:05:52,199 --> 00:05:53,399
I needed no one

73
00:05:53,399 --> 00:05:55,040
to protect me in this world.

74
00:05:56,399 --> 00:05:57,560
The world is vast,

75
00:05:57,680 --> 00:06:00,040
and I can do whatever I want.

76
00:06:02,279 --> 00:06:03,920
But after this,

77
00:06:05,560 --> 00:06:06,399
maybe

78
00:06:08,839 --> 00:06:10,040
I was wrong.

79
00:06:11,920 --> 00:06:13,160
Whatever you want to do,

80
00:06:14,120 --> 00:06:15,480
I'll support you.

81
00:06:18,680 --> 00:06:19,759
Easy to say.

82
00:06:29,920 --> 00:06:32,879
(Didn't expect the curse
to grow stronger.)

83
00:06:36,399 --> 00:06:40,160
(Why do I feel so strangely close to him?)

84
00:06:53,480 --> 00:06:53,839
Not good.

85
00:07:25,800 --> 00:07:27,079
What are you afraid of?

86
00:07:27,800 --> 00:07:29,360
Why did you

87
00:07:29,959 --> 00:07:31,360
bring me here?

88
00:07:32,839 --> 00:07:34,360
Don't worry,

89
00:07:34,800 --> 00:07:36,519
you're just bait.

90
00:07:37,240 --> 00:07:40,079
It's Su Wubing I want.

91
00:07:41,319 --> 00:07:41,680
You...

92
00:07:42,040 --> 00:07:43,240
Are you going after him?

93
00:07:45,639 --> 00:07:46,560
Little girl,

94
00:07:47,519 --> 00:07:49,240
it's not "going after".

95
00:07:49,800 --> 00:07:53,480
I just want his life.

96
00:07:57,040 --> 00:07:57,839
Let her go!

97
00:07:58,199 --> 00:07:58,639
Wubing.

98
00:08:00,519 --> 00:08:01,040
Wubing.

99
00:08:01,720 --> 00:08:03,079
He's coming for you.

100
00:08:05,639 --> 00:08:07,240
It's fine, you go first.

101
00:08:13,680 --> 00:08:16,079
Finally, you're here.

102
00:08:31,399 --> 00:08:33,360
Truly worthy of being the Immortal King.

103
00:08:33,759 --> 00:08:36,519
Even your mortal body has such an aura.

104
00:08:40,320 --> 00:08:42,240
The souls of the Immortal King
and Holy Maiden...

105
00:08:42,960 --> 00:08:44,639
Follow them, seize their souls,

106
00:08:44,960 --> 00:08:47,000
and our demons will
rule the Immortal Realm.

107
00:08:48,240 --> 00:08:51,279
(So the demons also entered
the Time-Space Array.)

108
00:08:57,480 --> 00:08:58,240
Su Wubing?

109
00:08:59,240 --> 00:09:00,519
What is he doing here?

110
00:09:05,639 --> 00:09:07,240
Seems you've been hunting me all along.

111
00:09:09,200 --> 00:09:10,720
We've sought you for ten thousand years,

112
00:09:10,720 --> 00:09:12,399
and finally, it wasn't in vain.

113
00:09:12,840 --> 00:09:14,639
You may be an ancient Immortal King,

114
00:09:14,759 --> 00:09:17,679
but now you're only Yellow-level.

115
00:09:18,240 --> 00:09:20,519
Perfect time to take your soul.

116
00:09:22,080 --> 00:09:23,080
I'll let you

117
00:09:23,799 --> 00:09:24,919
have three moves.

118
00:09:26,120 --> 00:09:27,480
Ancient God Sect,

119
00:09:27,559 --> 00:09:28,919
acting for Heaven.

120
00:09:29,039 --> 00:09:31,320
Today I'll take your life.

121
00:09:40,480 --> 00:09:41,720
The Immortal King just awoke.

122
00:09:41,960 --> 00:09:43,360
I must strike a killing blow.

123
00:09:52,279 --> 00:09:52,879
First move.

124
00:09:53,720 --> 00:09:54,399
Impossible.

125
00:09:54,679 --> 00:09:55,360
That move

126
00:09:55,360 --> 00:09:57,000
should've drained
all your spiritual power.

127
00:10:04,720 --> 00:10:05,559
Second move.

128
00:10:06,159 --> 00:10:08,399
You... you're not Yellow-level?

129
00:10:51,600 --> 00:10:52,799
Three moves are done.

130
00:10:53,440 --> 00:10:54,159
Kneel

131
00:10:55,080 --> 00:10:55,879
or die.

132
00:10:57,240 --> 00:10:58,039
No way!

133
00:10:59,559 --> 00:11:00,759
Still stubborn.

134
00:11:02,200 --> 00:11:02,679
Fall.

135
00:11:07,279 --> 00:11:09,320
So it's really you.

136
00:11:33,809 --> 00:11:37,912
♪I defy heaven, fate,
and so-called immortality♪

137
00:11:37,912 --> 00:11:42,632
♪At last you say
we've been apart too long♪

138
00:11:42,632 --> 00:11:47,512
♪Unwilling, unyielding, I won't let go♪

139
00:11:47,512 --> 00:11:52,632
♪With you, even a dried sea
learns to embrace a stream♪

140
00:11:52,632 --> 00:11:57,032
♪If heaven divides us, I'll reunite us,
with love as our vessel♪

141
00:11:57,032 --> 00:12:01,712
♪If it forbids it, I'll shatter
the absurd Heavenly Dao♪

142
00:12:01,712 --> 00:12:07,112
♪Even if countless stars
turn into my foes♪

143
00:12:07,112 --> 00:12:13,092
♪To grow old with you, we burn
through the end of the long night♪
